  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Travel to the slopes by train</h2>
<p>From train tracks to ski tracks, step off and ski on. Enjoy stress-free travel, flexible luggage allowance and room to stretch out. Leave the planning to us and enjoy the journey.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13099593/jungfraubahn-ski-train.jpg" alt="Ski Train" data-udi="umb://media/e4dbc89ec44546d3bea78bddbbbb6946" /></p>
<h2>Reach resort by rail</h2>
<p>Thinking of travelling by train this winter to some of Europe's best loved resorts? Then jump on board with an Inghams ski holiday by train. </p>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/search-results?from=QQS" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="?from=QQS">All train travel deals</a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Our ski holidays by train</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;">Next stop? A ski holiday of a lifetime. Experience an effortless journey when you travel by train to these popular ski resorts. See all the countries and their resorts that you can reach by train for your winter holiday. </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h3>Switzerland</h3>
<img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13100688/new-swis-rail.jpg" alt="swissrail" data-udi="umb://media/7040457ee3f34b5385e4f58ce01163cd" />
<p><span>With trains arriving at multiple resorts from </span><a data-udi="umb://document/a95de5322c984f85bcf0f013c457e8df" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/switzerland/graubunden-ski-region/davos" title="Davos">Davos</a><span> to </span><a data-udi="umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/switzerland/zermatt" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a><span>, viewing the mighty Matterhorn as your wind towards the Swiss Alps is unbeatable.</span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/bc1bd76cbabc4e7f8eb9be63f059ec2c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bc1bd76cbabc4e7f8eb9be63f059ec2c}" title="Switzerland ski holidays by rail" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-="">Find Out More</a></div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h3>Austria</h3>
<img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13100686/new-austria-rail.jpg" alt="austriarail" data-udi="umb://media/9d51cd09a29748fa95271b345d5310d0" />
<p><span>Avid skiers have long been keen to tackle the slopes of </span><a data-udi="umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/austria/arlberg-ski-area/st-anton" title="St Anton">St Anton</a><span>. Visit St Anton for your next ski trip and sit back, stretch out your legs and un-wind on the train as you make your way home from an intense week's skiing at this challenging resort. </span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/52ceff26b77f44c191c54542131586df" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52ceff26b77f44c191c54542131586df}" title="Austria ski holidays by rail" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Find Out More</a></div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h3>France</h3>
<img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13100687/new-france-rail.jpg" alt="francerail" data-udi="umb://media/b6b4cbce266947bbb6b2c33feb857fe3" />
<p><span>With only The Channel between us, France is often the first destination we think of for a ski holiday. Go from London to many French ski resorts by train, including <a data-udi="umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/france/la-rosi%C3%A8re" title="La Rosière">La Rosiere</a>, ideal for families or <a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/france/tignes-val-d-isere-ski-area/val-disere" title="Val d'Isere">Val d'Isere</a>, great for Après ski seekers. </span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/e4af3a3602bd41f7bf3e716613b877d9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e4af3a3602bd41f7bf3e716613b877d9}" title="France ski holidays by rail" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="#">Find Out More</a></div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2>Eurostar snow train</h2>
<p>Season 2023/24 we saw the Eurostar snow train back again which took passengers (including many of Inghams) from London St Pancras International Station on to resorts across Europe. With both Standard and Premier Classes on the Eurostar, comfort and choice are guaranteed all the way.</p>
<p>You could stay connected with free WiFi, indulge in onboard refreshments and make the most of generous luggage allowance. A first-class start to a snowy escape. Read more about the <a data-udi="umb://document/2bf29261e6e747a98423e8b40c1d21ea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2bf29261e6e747a98423e8b40c1d21ea}" title="Eurostar Snow Train">Eurostar Snow Train</a>.</p>
<h2>Be part of the change:</h2>
<p>The places you visit as part of your Inghams holiday are special, and it’s our responsibility to keep them that way, long into the future. Switching the plane for a train can reduce the carbon footprint of your holiday considerably. We want to make it as easy as possible for our customers to take the train, so we are offering rail travel to 4 countries across Europe. </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/67e40dbb55ff45098496ea2e7eee1f72" href="/{localLink:umb://document/67e40dbb55ff45098496ea2e7eee1f72}" class="c-btn">Sustainability with Inghams</a></p>
<p><img src="/media/13099193/eurostar-snow-6-838x300.jpg" alt="traintravel" data-udi="umb://media/757d05a8878648b6bff47483a20636cc" /></p>
<h4>Transfer details: </h4>
<p><span>Your transfer will normally be by coach, rail or included car hire depending on your resort. Transfer are included in your package. </span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/9b67579eaa2748aeae6357891f20ff01" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b67579eaa2748aeae6357891f20ff01}?from=QQS" title="Transfers" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="?from=QQS">Transfers</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to book your holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Simply give us a call to book your holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? We’ve got you covered. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
